headline: Lamb Weston Issues New Global Sustainability Report
summary: EAGLE, Idaho, June 11, 2025--With a focus on Making Fries and Making Strides, Lamb Weston Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: LW) issued its annual Global Sustainability Report today, providing updates on the company’s performance against key sustainability and people initiatives during its fiscal year 2024.
